Package com.darkfoxdev.tesi.targetlint.checks.operations

This package contains the check operations: the processing unit of a Check.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CheckOperation
    The type Check Operation.
    GroupAndExecuteCheckOperation<T>
    This check groups the input matches in different sets using the grouping predicate, and then executes a list of check operations on every set.
    MatchNumberCheckOperation
    This class provides check operations for numeric comparison on how many matches are found.
    ReferenceMatchCheckOperation<T>
    This check operation is defined by a second target and an operation of type Function<Match,T>.
    TargetFilterAsCheckOperation
    Provides a way to reuse target filters as check operations.
